Description:
You find a pedestal with a strange orb on top that is anchored to the pedestal. Next to the pedestal you see a stone tablet that explains how it works.

It seems to be an orb of corruption and to unanchor it you have to recharge it completely.

To do so, you have to put your hand on a glyphed tile on the pedestal. This will drain the life force of that person until the orb is fully recharged.
